PART 1: QR/NQR ending distribution from vertex 0
======================================================================

  P_3: h₀ = 1
    Ending at QR: 0 = 1 × 0
    Ending at NQR: 1 = 1 × 1
    Ratio NQR/QR per vertex: inf
    QR end counts: all equal = 0
    NQR end counts: all equal = 1

  P_7: h₀ = 27
    Ending at QR: 3 = 3 × 1
    Ending at NQR: 24 = 3 × 8
    Ratio NQR/QR per vertex: 8
    QR end counts: all equal = 1
    NQR end counts: all equal = 8

  P_11: h₀ = 8645
    Ending at QR: 3140 = 5 × 628
    Ending at NQR: 5505 = 5 × 1101
    Ratio NQR/QR per vertex: 1101/628
    QR end counts: all equal = 628
    NQR end counts: all equal = 1101

  P_19: h₀ = 61720828785
    Ending at QR: 27362064852 = 9 × 3040229428
    Ending at NQR: 34358763933 = 9 × 3817640437
    Ratio NQR/QR per vertex: 3817640437/3040229428
    QR end counts: all equal = 3040229428
    NQR end counts: all equal = 3817640437

